        "symptom": "Shortness of breath",
        "description": "Difficulty in breathing or feeling winded, even during mild exertion, as the heart struggles to pump effectively."
      },
      {
        "symptom": "Fatigue",
        "description": "Extreme tiredness and low energy levels, resulting from the body's lack of adequate oxygen supply."
